\">Stop Trading on Feeling.\nStart Trading on System.</h1><p>Trading on emotion drains accounts. Trading on a system backtested 5+ years generates consistent profit. BerkahKarya Algo Trading: automatic entry/exit signals, disciplined execution, no more staying up to monitor charts.</p><div class=\"HeroSection_buttons__AAb79\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/6285732740006?text=Hello%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20BerkahKarya%20Algo%20Trading\" class=\"HeroSection_primary__XoIi7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">💬 Free Strategy Consultation</a><a href=\"#features\" class=\"HeroSection_secondary__W4nQd\">View Strategy</a></div><div class=\"HeroSection_strip__3xnuY\"><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>Setup &lt;5 menit</span></div><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>Garansi 7 hari</span></div><div class=\"HeroSection_stripItem___vGpb\"><span>✓</span><span>Support via Telegram</span></div></div></div><div class=\"HeroSection_characterWrap__voqYh\"><div class=\"CharacterAvatar_wrapper__0IoSK CharacterAvatar_glow__HUnmw CharacterAvatar_float__W3JJX CharacterAvatar_hero__QGyAr \"><img alt=\"Vilona — AI Trading Analyst\" fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"280\" height=\"280\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"CharacterAvatar_image__EmH_M\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fcharacters%2Fvilona-side.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"ProblemSection_wrap__QO54b\" style=\"padding:5rem 0\"><div class=\"ProblemSection_container__FqN12\"><p class=\"ProblemSection_hook__B4YPn\">Why do most retail traders keep losing even after years of learning?</p><div class=\"ProblemSection_grid__Zo7yR\"><div class=\"ProblemSection_pain___4ZRV\"><div class=\"ProblemSection_iconWrap__RUsYT\">😰</div><p>Emotions ruin strategy —